Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_check_output_pin_constant(25.10)    init_check_output_pin_constant(25.10)

Name
       init_check_output_pin_constant

Syntax
        init_check_output_pin_constant  {0 | 1 }

       Type: Boolean

       Default: 1

       Stops  the Verilog reader if any output (or inout) signal pins have any
       1'b0 or 1'b1 constants that would cause shorts to power/ground.

       The default value of this boolean variable is TRUE or 1.

Related Information
              * init_design

              * setCheckMode

